'''Kamal Hachkar''' (  yavutse ku ya 25 Gashyantare 1977), ni umukinnyi wa firime ukomoka muri [[Maroke]] [[Ubufaransa|n'ubufaransa]], akaba n'umuhanga <ref>https://pro.festivalscope.com/director/kamal-hachkar</ref>.  Kamal azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa filime ''yamamaye cyane Tinghir-Yeruzalemu: The Echoes of mellah'' .<ref>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium.MAGAZINE-muslim-moroccan-director-tries-to-crack-the-mystery-of-jews-who-left-his-homeland-1.9183639</ref> 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 25 Gashyantare 1977 i Tinghir, muri [[Maroke|Maroc]] mu muryango wa Berber<ref>http://icarusfilms.com/if-jer</ref>.  Afite amezi atandatu gusa, yavuye muri [[Maroc]] ari kumwe na nyina yerekeza mu [[Bufaransa]], aho se yakoraga nk'umukozi kuva mu 1968. Icyakora, yagiye asura Tinghir buri gihe mu biruhuko<ref>https://www.festivalmarrakech.info/en/personnalite/kamal-hachkar/</ref>. Kamal yabonye impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu mateka yo hagati y’isi y’abayisilamu muri kaminuza ya Sorbonne . Mu 2005, yabaye umwarimu nyuma yo gutanga icyemezo cy'ubuhanga bwo kwigisha amashuri yisumbuye.<ref>https://www.festivalmarrakech.info/personnalite/kamal-hachkar/</ref>  

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2013, Kamal yakoze umushinga wa documentaire yambere, ''Tinghir-Yerusalemu: Les Échos du mellah'' <ref>https://telquel.ma/2020/12/18/kamal-hachkar-cest-un-fantasme-de-mes-ennemis-je-ne-pourrai-jamais-e%CC%82tre-un-agent-du-mossad_1705509</ref>.<ref>https://insidearabia.com/tinghir-jerusalem-kamal-hachkar-talks-about-his-film/</ref>  Iyi filime yashyizweho mu gihe cyo kurinda [[Abafaransa]] muri [[Maroc]] ivuga ku buzima n’imibereho y’imiryango y’abayisilamu ya Berber n’abayahudi i Tinghir mu bihe bikomeye.<ref>http://africultures.com/php/?nav=personne&no=31199</ref> Nubwo, byari ingingo itavugwaho rumwe muri [[Maroc]], yanenzwe n’abayisilamu.  Nyuma, Ishyaka ry'Ubutabera n'Iterambere naryo ryinjiye mu kunegura bavuga ko ari ubutumire bwo guhuza umubano hagati ya [[Isiraheli]]. Icyakora, iyi filime yakiriwe neza ndetse n'ibihembo byinshi mu iserukiramuco rya sinema ry’igihugu cya [[Maroc]].<ref>https://festivalfilmeduc.net/en/films/realisation/kamal-hachkar/</ref><ref>https://www.arabiskefilmdager.no/en/film/2021/in-your-eyes-i-see-my-country</ref> 

